This paper focuses on the use of social bots to study the impact of user preference on news consumption and the formation of social networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also touches on topics related to sociology (cs.SOC), information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), and cybersecurity (cs.CYBER) in terms of designing and deploying the social bots.
